                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                    <h5 class="home-title">What is AirMed <span class="blue-word">Foundation</span>?</h5>
                    <p class="home-paragraph">Airmed foundation is a secure way to transfer or share medical records (or any sensitive document) between pairs, uses <strong>InterPlanetary Filesystem</strong> technology for the transfer and storage of records and <strong>Hyperledger Fabric</strong> for the storage of encrypted transactions, both technologies guarantee the immutability of the data, allowing to register all kinds of modifications. This works totally decentralized.</p>
