                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                    <h5 class="home-title">How does it work?</h5>
                    <p class="home-paragraph">There are two ways to use Airmed, the first and easiest is to upload a file and share it through the hash address that returns the system, being able to download it to any <strong>InterPlanetary Filesystem</strong>  client that is connected to the public network. The second and more complex way is using identities to encrypt the file and restricting access by a specific person, for this process, we have created the following <a href="/guide">tutorial</a>.</p>
